{"source_id": "dm-zhao-yuanlong", "source_type": "dm_user", "message_id": "om_x100b573004ca70b8e116e4c5f97bf09", "chat_id": "ou_cfbb3a081027568887b6063c4f56d50a", "chat_type": "unknown", "sender_id": "ou_cfbb3a081027568887b6063c4f56d50a", "sender_name": "Zhao Yuanlong", "direction": "incoming", "created_at": "2026-02-02 14:30", "content": "为什么其它客群都是一样的", "payload": {"content": "为什么其它客群都是一样的", "create_time": "2026-02-02 14:30", "deleted": false, "message_id": "om_x100b573004ca70b8e116e4c5f97bf09", "msg_type": "text", "sender": {"id": "ou_cfbb3a081027568887b6063c4f56d50a", "id_type": "open_id", "name": "Zhao Yuanlong", "sender_type": "user", "tenant_key": "1503d1037d07977c"}, "updated": false}}
{"source_id": "dm-zhao-yuanlong", "source_type": "dm_user", "message_id": "om_x100b573003a03cace2d15d79ff33337", "chat_id": "ou_cfbb3a081027568887b6063c4f56d50a", "chat_type": "unknown", "sender_id": "ou_cfbb3a081027568887b6063c4f56d50a", "sender_name": "Zhao Yuanlong", "direction": "incoming", "created_at": "2026-02-02 14:31", "content": "```SQL\nclass Scorer:\n    base_odds = math.exp(3)\n\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        min_score=400,\n        max_score=1_200,\n        pdo=50,\n        base_odds=base_odds,\n        base=650,\n    ):\n        self.A = pdo / math.log(2)\n        self.B = base - math.log(base_odds) * self.A\n        self.min_score = min_score\n        self.max_score = max_score\n        self.lower_proba = 1 / (math.exp((max_score - self.B) / self.A) + 1)\n        self.upper_proba = 1 / (math.exp((min_score - self.B) / self.A) + 1)\n\n    def _to_score(self, proba):\n        if proba < self.lower_proba:\n            return self.max_score\n        if proba > self.upper_proba:\n            return self.min_score\n        return round(self.A * math.log((1 - proba) / proba) + self.B)\n\n    def to_score(self, proba):\n        if np.isscalar(proba):\n            return self._to_score(proba)\n        return np.vectorize(self._to_score)(proba)\n\n    def _to_proba(self, score):\n        return 1 / (1 + math.exp((score - self.B) / self.A))\n\n    def to_proba(self, score):\n        if np.isscalar(score):\n            return self._to_proba(score)\n        return np.vectorize(self._to_proba)(score)\n\n```\n\n上面是a卡的， b卡用的转换函数和a卡一样吗？", "payload": {"content": "```SQL\nclass Scorer:\n    base_odds = math.exp(3)\n\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        min_score=400,\n        max_score=1_200,\n        pdo=50,\n        base_odds=base_odds,\n        base=650,\n    ):\n        self.A = pdo / math.log(2)\n        self.B = base - math.log(base_odds) * self.A\n        self.min_score = min_score\n        self.max_score = max_score\n        self.lower_proba = 1 / (math.exp((max_score - self.B) / self.A) + 1)\n        self.upper_proba = 1 / (math.exp((min_score - self.B) / self.A) + 1)\n\n    def _to_score(self, proba):\n        if proba < self.lower_proba:\n            return self.max_score\n        if proba > self.upper_proba:\n            return self.min_score\n        return round(self.A * math.log((1 - proba) / proba) + self.B)\n\n    def to_score(self, proba):\n        if np.isscalar(proba):\n            return self._to_score(proba)\n        return np.vectorize(self._to_score)(proba)\n\n    def _to_proba(self, score):\n        return 1 / (1 + math.exp((score - self.B) / self.A))\n\n    def to_proba(self, score):\n        if np.isscalar(score):\n            return self._to_proba(score)\n        return np.vectorize(self._to_proba)(score)\n\n```\n\n上面是a卡的， b卡用的转换函数和a卡一样吗？", "create_time": "2026-02-02 14:31", "deleted": false, "message_id": "om_x100b573003a03cace2d15d79ff33337", "msg_type": "post", "sender": {"id": "ou_cfbb3a081027568887b6063c4f56d50a", "id_type": "open_id", "name": "Zhao Yuanlong", "sender_type": "user", "tenant_key": "1503d1037d07977c"}, "updated": false}}
